dc_title_s: Morris County, New Jersey highways 1967 map 6
dc_description_s: Base map of Morris County. Sheet six of a six sheet map. Prepared by the New Jersey State Highway Department, Division of Planning in cooperation with the U. S. Department of Commerce, Bureau of Public Roads. Series includes 35 insets of major road junctures. This sheet includes legend showing road system designations, railroads, road types, navigation and drainage, bridges and tunnels, boundaries, general culture features. State highways as of Dec. 31, 1967. Culture, county roads and municipal streets are as of 1940.
